data.description: BUYERS CREDIT UP TO $15,000 DEPENDING ON OFFER. MOTIVATED SELLER!! Beautiful new construction, ranch style home sitting on ONE ACRE! Located in the highly sought after Sanger country side. Recently fully completed.This home has great curb appeal in a fabulous neighborhood all on oversized lots. As you walk in you'll be treated to stunning views of the living area, stone fireplace, oversized office with built in desk and a front common room. Open Kitchen with an oversized island, granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. Dining room that looks out to the back of the property. Primary bedroom has an ensuite with a stand alone tub, dual vanities, and a custom walk in closet. On the other side of the house you'll see two guest rooms and two full bathrooms. This lot is made to have your stand alone outdoor pergola, pool, or metal barn on either side of the home, making it very unique. Come see this gorgeous floor plan in the great Sanger Texas.
